147
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,000
The good news is that since then,

148
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:02,680
we've got more comfortable
talking about mental health,

149
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:06,120
with PSAs like this one from 2010
trying to destigmatize it.

150
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:08,879
In the all-American
health care system,

151
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:11,639
there is coverage for heart health,
care for cancer.

152
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:14,639
But the all-American brain
is getting lost in the shuffle.

153
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:18,279
Brain tumor, fine.
Brain disease, not so fine.

154
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,360
There's no stigma or discrimination
against the heart,

155
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,240
the liver, the kidney,
and the gallbladder.

156
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,160
Doesn't even have a job.

157
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,279
