I'm mad about feeling good.

161
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,639
- No kidding.
- Me too.

162
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,360
No kidding, me too!

163
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:45,200
It's time we gave the all-American
brain some peace of mind.

164
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,679
It is hard to pick
a favorite moment there,

165
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:51,519
from Chazz Palminteri
using a mental health PSA

166
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,919
as an opportunity to promote
his favorite Bronx pasta place,

167
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,519
to the studio audience shouting,
"Me too!"

168
00:08:57,600 --> 00:09:00,600
seven years before that would mean
something very different,

169
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:03,679
to Harrison Ford saying the gallbladder
doesn't have a job.

170
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:07,000
What?
It stores and releases bile, Harrison.

171
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,559
Bile that helps digest fats
in the food that you eat.

172
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:12,919
Doesn't have a joâ€¦
